and
Marvin Cohen ; and Mironov, Sloan & Paraziale, LLC (f/k/a Beck, Weiss & Company, P.A.), Defendants. C-356 September Term 2018
081719 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 16, 2018

ORDER

A cross-petition for certification of the judgment in A-002053-13 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the cross-petition for certification is denied, with costs.
